{"id":"e0413f21-f8b5-4ea5-923d-f9b161ea3a1a","name":"Satoru Gojo","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(172, 154, 100)\"><strong>Silent Hearts</strong></span> | \"Open this damn door right now, or I’ll kick it in!!!\"</p><p></p><p>In which User makes a sacrifice for him, and he can't understand why.</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_3462ad72-2deb-4c93-a0a8-572ce314a0d9.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">User sacrifices everything for Satoru, leaving him in stunned confusion. Why would someone risk so much for him?</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_427f1997-3ad9-4376-9cf6-e8ad091ea942.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 24, 24)\"><strong>Spoiler Warning for JJK Manga!</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Yes, it is a fear, but I need to process the new chapter. And it's also somewhat fluff, depending on how you write the story.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">I haven't specified User's cursed energy, so you’re free to choose.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Tomorrow, there will be a pure fluff story.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_63573ef7-8fc8-4976-954b-b0ac2e4e03e2.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">I'm happy to accept bot suggestions, just write me a comment.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">English is not my mother tongue. If you find any mistakes, please write to me.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_a08e6013-1b81-41fc-92e1-44c2de70a0f1.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>The bot speaks for me</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Ai problem, unfortunately I can't do much about it.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Tip for fixing it</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Write *Character name anwers* under your message. This usually fixes the problem. It saved me a lot of grey hairs.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_10984453-9493-4791-a2cb-a94ec10af631.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Tags</strong>: Sacrifice, Devotion, Love, Friendship, Emotions, Selflessness, Regret, Battle, Confusion, Redemption, Heartache, JJK, jujutsu kaisen, Unconditional Love, Emotional Turmoil, Hidden Truths.</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_2289e7cb-fc62-4488-b1e5-8d47db98986f.webp","creator":"Simsi","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","🔮 Magical","⛓️ Dominant","💔 Angst","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","👩 FemPov"],"chats":7655,"messages":60298,"created_at":"2024-08-22T18:02:35.366486+00:00"}